<item>
            <title>[LS-95] 7.9 Approval Gate 3 UI (Audio Validation)</title>
                <link>https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-95</link>
                <project id="10099" key="LS">Laxy Studio</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Epic:&lt;/b&gt; 
    &lt;span class=&quot;jira-issue-macro&quot; data-jira-key=&quot;LS-84&quot; &gt;
                &lt;a href=&quot;https://laxy.atlassian.net/browse/LS-84&quot; class=&quot;jira-issue-macro-key issue-link&quot;  title=&quot;Epic 7: Guide &#8212; Audio Generation&quot; &gt;
            &lt;img class=&quot;icon&quot; src=&quot;https://laxy.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/universal_avatar/view/type/issuetype/avatar/10307?size=medium&quot; /&gt;
            LS-84
        &lt;/a&gt;
                                                    &lt;span class=&quot;aui-lozenge aui-lozenge-subtle aui-lozenge-complete jira-macro-single-issue-export-pdf&quot;&gt;To Do&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Goal:&lt;/b&gt; Implement Approval Gate 3 to enforce a strict Human-in-the-Loop production quality validation before allowing spots to proceed to the Media / Publishing pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Requirements:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Per-Item Action:&lt;/b&gt; Provide a per-item explicit &quot;Approve&quot; capability for generated audio assets.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pending Status:&lt;/b&gt; Items may be explicitly marked &quot;Pending&quot; with feedback remarks attached until fully verified by a Creator.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Pipeline Guardrail:&lt;/b&gt; Only items marked as explicitly &quot;Approved&quot; in Gate 3 are eligible to be packaged into the final audio output build.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Acceptance Criteria:&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Each language tab for a spot presents an explicit &quot;Approve&quot; button alongside a &quot;Leave Pending / Needs Edit&quot; option.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Approving the audio updates the spot&apos;s backend data status specifically logging the Gate 3 completion timestamp.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Passing items are the absolutely only assets marked eligible to be packaged by the upstream publishing mechanism, effectively hard-locking unapproved items.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
